code: export function loadTweets(callback){var xhr=new XMLHttpRequest();var method='GET';var url="http://localhost:8000/api/tweets/";var responseType="json";xhr.responseType=responseType;xhr.open(method,url);xhr.onload=function(){callback(xhr.response,xhr.status);};xhr.onerror=function(e){callback({"message":"the request was an error"},400);};xhr.send();}
